claim.claim-text:
32. A system for transferring electronic information, comprising: 
a subscription device comprising: 
a first processor; and 
a first storage device in communication with the first processor and storing instructions adapted to be executed by the first processor to: 
transmit a file of electronic information according to a subscription; and 
receive a certificate certifying that a portion of the file of electronic information has been rendered unusable; and 


a consumer device comprising: 
a second processor; and 
a second storage device in communication with the second processor and storing instructions adapted to be executed by the second processor to: 
receive the file of electronic information; 
receive a command to transmit a portion of the file of electronic information; 
determine whether the portion of the file of electronic information should be automatically copied and rendered unusable; 
automatically copy the portion of the file of electronic information to create a copied file of electronic information; 
transmit the copied file; 
render the portion of the file of electronic information unusable; and 
transmit the certificate to the subscription device.
